    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 power plant. This unit benefits from a recently serviced Double VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's known torsional stress points. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension remains taut with upgraded bushings, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow aluminum radiator. Minor cosmetic patina consistent with age, but mechanically robust and ready for the apex.",
