      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye will note minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery has been treated regularly and shows only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s side. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule, with a comprehensive folder of service receipts included. Recent updates include a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires and a complete brake fluid flush. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. This is a turn-key example for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been respected and cared for throughout its life.",
      "price": 34800.0,
