      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and handles the road beautifully! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great and drives smooth, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
